###
@modelId = {{train.response.body.modelId}}



### get training-status
# @name train-status
GET {{api}}/train/{{modelId}}
Content-Type: application/json
X-App-Id: {{appId}}


### cancel training
# @name cancel-training
POST {{api}}/train/{{modelId}}/cancel
Content-Type: application/json
X-App-Id: {{appId}}

### predict for sentence
# @name predict
POST {{api}}/predict/{{modelId}}
Content-Type: application/json
